author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be the end of the Internet. AI technology has taken over nearly every aspect of what we do both online and offline and with privacy and security taking a backseat it's too a point that the cost is now being passed onto all of us (even if we don't ever use it). What can we do to fight back and how can we use this stuff somewhat responsibly? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: We've Reached The End Of The Internet...
